text: hey everyone its mark Wiens with
migration ology calm and let me tell you
Hawaii is a beautiful place with
gorgeous beaches and stunning green
mountains but it's all secondary when
you compare it to Hawaiian food
oh I included some of the tastiest most
delicious food I've ever had in my
entire life
so when you come to a Hawaii make sure
you come with an empty stomach and a
desire to devour as much as you can
handle
spam okay it's not made in Hawaii but it
is perfected in Hawaii a block of rice
topped with spam and wrapped in seaweed
doesn't get much better for another
breakfast favorite get a plate of
Hawaiian Portuguese sausage with eggs
and rice for a beach lunch you'll want a
Hawaiian plate lunch
the trio of teriyaki barbeque chicken
rice and macaroni salad I also love the
deep fried mahi mahi version of a
Hawaiian flavor a loco moco is a giant
foam box of rice topped with hamburger
patties fried eggs and doused in brown
gravy if you're a meat lover the Chinese
Hawaiian style barbecue ribs are divine
bites of glory that slide off the bone
and burst with flavor
Kalen is a chinese inspired dish of
fried white rice noodles mixed with beef
and a few assorted veggies one of the
Giants of Hawaiian food is poking cubes
of raw fish mixed with an assortment of
tasty other ingredients poki is so good
you might forget about peach altogether
mussels pokey is also delicious mussels
marinated chilies soy sauce and green
onions
try ocean salad seafood salad made from
slivers of wakame and agar agar the
traditional Hawaiian staple is POI a
thick paste made from pounded taro root
another traditional Hawaiian food
favorite is Lau Lau pork chicken or fish
wrapped in taro leaves smoke and steamed
the island wouldn't be the same without
sweet treats either malasadas are
perfect Portuguese doughnuts made of
soft pillows of deep-fried dough dipped
in show
a layer of chocolate pudding topped with
coconut creamy haupia and whipped cream
is about as sexy as desserts come lastly
there's shave ice
a Hawaiian culinary giant have finally
shaved ice piled into a cup and doused
in sweet tropical fruit flavored syrups
so there you have it 16 of the most
delicious Hawaiian foods miss eating
these ambrosia Hawaiian foods and your
visit to Hawaii will be incomplete
